Is it possible to expose a selectionOverlayTransitionBuilder in TextFormField/TextField, allowing developers to fully customize the toolbar’s transition?

Currently, the forced fade-in animation (with no corresponding fade-out animation) negatively affects UI elements like blur effects. In some cases, it can be more disruptive than having no animation at all.

This enhancement would offer more flexibility for developers to implement smoother, more consistent transitions, improving the overall user experience.

